<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pourquoi nous choisir - YuniGate</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
  
    <style>
        .hover-lift {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .hover-lift:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }
        .dark .card {
            background: #1f2937;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Toggle pour tester le mode sombre -->
    

    <section class="py-16 bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-secondary-800">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
            <!-- Section Title -->
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                    Pourquoi <span class="text-primary-500">nous choisir</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    YuniGate se distingue par son expertise et son engagement envers la réussite de chaque étudiant.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Reasons Grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
                <!-- Expertise locale -->
                <div class="card p-6 hover-lift" 
                     x-data="{ hover: false }"
                     x-on:mouseenter="hover = true" 
                     x-on:mouseleave="hover = false">
                    <div 
                        class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-5 text-primary-500 transition-all duration-300"
                        x-bind:class="hover ? 'bg-primary-500 text-white' : 'bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30'"
                    >
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Expertise locale</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
                        Notre équipe dispose d'une connaissance approfondie du système éducatif marocain et des procédures administratives locales.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Service sur mesure -->
                <div class="card p-6 hover-lift" 
                     x-data="{ hover: false }"
                     x-on:mouseenter="hover = true" 
                     x-on:mouseleave="hover = false">
                    <div 
                        class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-5 text-primary-500 transition-all duration-300"
                        x-bind:class="hover ? 'bg-primary-500 text-white' : 'bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30'"
                    >
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Service sur mesure</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
                        Chaque étudiant bénéficie d'un accompagnement personnalisé, adapté à ses besoins spécifiques et à son profil académique.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Réseau universitaire -->
                <div class="card p-6 hover-lift" 
                     x-data="{ hover: false }"
                     x-on:mouseenter="hover = true" 
                     x-on:mouseleave="hover = false">
                    <div 
                        class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-5 text-primary-500 transition-all duration-300"
                        x-bind:class="hover ? 'bg-primary-500 text-white' : 'bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30'"
                    >
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Réseau universitaire</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
                        Notre partenariat avec les meilleures universités privées du Maroc vous offre un accès privilégié à des formations de qualité.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Accompagnement complet -->
                <div class="card p-6 hover-lift" 
                     x-data="{ hover: false }"
                     x-on:mouseenter="hover = true" 
                     x-on:mouseleave="hover = false">
                    <div 
                        class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-5 text-primary-500 transition-all duration-300"
                        x-bind:class="hover ? 'bg-primary-500 text-white' : 'bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30'"
                    >
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.35 3.836c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 00.75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 00-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0113.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m8.9-4.414c.376.023.75.05 1.124.08 1.131.094 1.976 1.057 1.976 2.192V16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0118 18.75h-2.25m-7.5-10.5H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V18.75m-7.5-10.5h6.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.375m-8.25-3l1.5 1.5 3-3.75" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Accompagnement complet</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
                        Du premier contact jusqu'à l'obtention de votre diplôme, nous restons à vos côtés pour vous soutenir dans toutes vos démarches.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Statistics Section -->
            <div class="mt-16 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hidden">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-500 mb-2">98%</div>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">Taux de satisfaction</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-500 mb-2">500+</div>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">Étudiants accompagnés</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary-500 mb-2">10+</div>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">Universités partenaires</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>